      "factId": "hz.web.c1b24ff8542e0b21.fact.2",
      "kind": "bullet",
      "text": "Topping out at 12,950 group members and a whopping 33.3K photo submissions, our judges had the privilege to review some truly stunning work submitted by the Flickr community.",
